oracle.mapviewer.share.stylex
Class BarChartStyleModel

java.lang.Object
  oracle.mapviewer.share.style.AbstractStyleModel
      oracle.mapviewer.share.stylex.BarChartStyleModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, StyleModel
public class BarChartStyleModel
extends AbstractStyleModel

Model class for BarCharStyle. On a bar chart map, each geographic area is associated with a bar chart. All the bar charts on a map share the same scale.

See Also:
